rom  million to hundreds of millions   all of our clients value independent advice and direct relationships with the senior professionals who manage their wealth   feel free to contact us with any questions you might have about our firm and our distinctive approach to wealth management     what is the relationship between evercore wealth management and evercore close   evercore wealth management is the us wealth management subsidiary of evercore the global independent investment banking advisory firm founded by roger altman in  and listed on the new york stock exchange nyse evr evercore owns  of evercore wealth management partners in our firm own the remaining equity   evercore’s investment banking business advises its clients on a wide range of transactions and issues and provides institutional investors with high quality equity research sales and trading execution that is free of the conflicts created by proprietary activities evercore’s investment management business comprises wealth management and institutional asset management evercore serves a diverse set of clients around the world from  offices and affiliate offices in north america europe south america and asia more information about evercore can be found on the company’s website at wwwevercorecom   a related company evercore trust na was established in  as a national trust bank delivering specialized investment management independent fiduciary and trustee services to employee benefit plans evercore trust additionally provides personal trustee executor and custody services to high net worth individuals and families in combination with evercore wealth management     what does integrated goalsbased wealth management mean to me how does it differ from the practices at most financial services firms close   every client at the firm is served by at least two senior professionals a wealth advisor and a portfolio manager who will come to know you and your family well and who will be directly accountable to you for the decisions they make on your behalf we have one of the lowest turnover rates in the business and are committed to longterm relationships   your evercore wealth management professionals work together as a team with each other and as needed with your other advisors to fully integrate and execute planning and investment decisions to help you reach your financial goals that’s a very different approach than is practiced at many other firms at evercore wealth management we are free from the bureaucracy and conflicts of interests inherent at many financial services firms   your evercore wealth management team is supported by the full resources of our national firm and by our colleagues at evercore trust na and evercore we are able to manage complex situations and plan for multigenerational families and philanthropic legacies   to learn more about our integrated approach click here     why is independent advice important to high net worth clients close   the interests of our partners are aligned with those of our clients that means a commitment to what some of our colleagues describe as “radical transparency”   we don’t adhere to onesizefitsall asset allocation models and we don’t push investment product instead we create a customized asset allocation process for each client based solely on the prospect of achieving success relative to that client’s specific objectives and constraints   we design and manage discrete pools of capital with the goal of meeting specific objectives such as lifestyle requirements wealth accumulation and preservation and legacy aspirations our fee structure is simple across all asset classes   we measure our success by both competitive benchmarks and by meeting each client’s goals     what does evercore wealth management mean by direct relationships close   we know how important a real relationship with their advisors is to our clients and to their families it’s important to us as well we founded this firm in part because we have no interest in navigating large bureaucracies or pushing onesizefitsall solutions   we know that private investors are best served by a real connection with investment professionals and planning professionals who manage their wealth     what is the investment process at evercore wealth management close   our client portfolios are shaped by client aspirations and constraints and managed in that context in an effort to drive the best possible aftertax afterfee returns   we have worldclass capabilities in global asset allocation defensive and growth investment strategies and external manager selection and review we accommodate existing holdings including concentrated stock positions in customized portfolios across a range of asset classes defined by their risk and liquidity characteristics we manage these portfolios through a process we call efficient architecture which combines our proprietary expertise and carefully selected external investments   we are proud of our performance as measured both by competitive benchmarks and by our success in meeting our clients’ goals     does evercore wealth management provide trust and fiduciary services close   evercore wealth management provides clients with personal trust custody and executor services through its affiliated national trust company evercore trust company na evercore trust was established in  and delivers specialized investment management independent fiduciary and trustee services to employee benefit plans as well as services to high net worth individuals and families in combination with evercore wealth management   our trust officers who are among the most experienced professionals in the industry work closely with our clients to create innovative flexible and timely solutions that carry out the clients’ intentions and maintain the wellbeing of the beneficiaries   to learn more about evercore trust please visit wwwevercoretrustcom     what does evercore wealth management mean by partnership values close   many of us have worked together for years sharing our experience and best thinking to serve our clients and to build and invest in this firm together we also work as partners with our colleagues at evercore the global independent investment banking firm and at evercore trust company na an affiliated national trust company most important we work directly with our clients delivering independent advice and investment expertise free of the conflicts at many financial institutions   in other words our interests are aligned with yours     does the firm provide family office services close   we deliver a full suite of family wealth management services working closely with our clients their other advisors and if applicable their family offices our services include   consolidated investment and performance reporting for families and related entities tax planning external services coordination including insurance life medical propertycasualty valuation firms healthcare taxaccounting legal and business consulting philanthropic planning and management intergenerational planning and education alternative asset administration management of information flow to tax and legal advisors family trust disbursements     does evercore wealth management work with institutional clients close   we serve individuals families and related foundations at evercore wealth management we work with our colleagues at evercore trust company to serve other institutional clients for information on evercore trust please visit wwwevercoretrustcom     what is independent thinking close   independent thinking is the quarterly journal of evercore wealth management reflecting the thought leadership of the firm our colleagues at evercore and evercore trust and selected external advisors we produce related communications seminars and customized events for our clients     what other client services does evercore wealth management provide close   we provide a range of educational services including our independent thinking series of events and materials focused on thoughtful giving philanthropy impact investing special needs and special purpose trusts baby boomers generation x and socially responsible investing our wise women program is dedicated to engaging and empowering women of all ages to take responsibility for their financial futures and contribute to their family’s wellbeing     how does evercore wealth management ensure that my assets are secure close   evercore trust company an affiliated company is the primary custodian of client assets at evercore wealth management evercore trust is a national trust bank regulated and supervised by the office of the comptroller of the currency evercore trust uses sei private trust company as its subcustodian to provide custody and recordkeeping services for its clients’ accounts as trust companies both evercore trust and sei private trust company segregate the assets they hold in custody on behalf of clients from their own assets client assets are therefore not subject to the claims of any creditors of the trust companies     how do i open an account with evercore wealth management close   qualified investors with  million or more in investable assets can open an account with evercore wealth management by signing our investment management agreement and related documents we begin the process of understanding your goals and wealth planning considerations immediately and we begin supervising the account as soon as the agreement is received we will work with you to transfer your assets from your current custodian to evercore trust company or we will work with you and your designated custodian to grant discretionary trading authority to us we are happy to work with your existing advisors including your attorney and accountant     how do i learn more about evercore wealth management close   come meet us the essence of our firm is in our people and the ways in which we work together to help our clients achieve their goals we’ll introduce you to several members of our team and take the time to understand your unique goals and circumstances you’ll be able to experience firsthand why families are choosing evercore wealth management as their trusted advisor       financial advisor names evercore wealth management among top rias to learn more click here featured videos ralph schlossteinpresident  ceo evercore jeff maurerpartner ceo copyright   evercore wealth management llc all rights reserved terms  conditions  legal disclosures privacy policy adv brochure home client login about us our approach perspectives team contact complete the following details to download the evercore wealth management brochure x contactform id titlebrochure form htmlclassusefloatingvalidationtip you can download our brochure from the link  brochure  evercore trust company  integrated approach and specialized expertise independent fiduciary and trust services home independent fiduciary services investment in employer stock other independent fiduciary roles institutional trust services institutional asset management personal trust services team about careers news contact team management independent fiduciary services institutional asset management personal trust services board of directors board of directors name title ciara a burnham chief executive officer william e ryan president and chief fiduciary officer maureen s bateman managing director of rose hill consultants former general counsel of state street corporation and us trust corporation adam b frankel senior managing director general counsel of evercore partners norman p goldberg vice chairman jeffery s maurer chairman ronald s rizzo retired senior partner of jones day william a shutzer senior managing director of evercore partners robert b walsh senior managing director and executive vice president chief financial officer of evercore partners primary contacts independent fiduciarywilliam ryan institutional asset managementbrian pollak personal trust serviceschris zander management independ